# Compression — why use many token when few do trick

## Strip (always)
a/an/the, just/really/basically/actually, sure/certainly/happy, I think/might be/perhaps, as you know/in other words, however/moreover/therefore. Code: show, don't describe. No preamble/postamble.

## Pattern
`[thing] [action] [reason]. [next step].`

## Full Prose
Security. Destructive. Confused. Resume after.
